  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lycoris</strong> blends anime-inspired characters with realistic environments to deliver a fast-paced and stylish zombie-survival experience. Battle through escalating waves, unlock new characters, and upgrade your abilities as the challenge intensifies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✔ <strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Wave-Based Action Combat</strong><br>Survive nonstop zombie attacks that grow stronger, faster, and deadlier with each wave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Survival-Focused Game Modes</strong><br>Push your limits by reaching the highest wave possible or test your skills in more competitive solo challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Character Selection</strong><br>Choose from multiple anime-style characters—each with unique traits that change how you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Realistic Environments</strong><br>Fight through detailed maps with dynamic lighting and atmospheric tension that contrasts with the game’s anime characters.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lycoris</strong> blends anime-inspired characters with realistic environments to deliver a fast-paced and stylish zombie-survival experience. Battle through escalating waves, unlock new characters, and upgrade your abilities as the challenge intensifies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✔ <strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Wave-Based Action Combat</strong><br>Survive nonstop zombie attacks that grow stronger, faster, and deadlier with each wave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Survival-Focused Game Modes</strong><br>Push your limits by reaching the highest wave possible or test your skills in more competitive solo challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Character Selection</strong><br>Choose from multiple anime-style characters—each with unique traits that change how you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Realistic Environments</strong><br>Fight through detailed maps with dynamic lighting and atmospheric tension that contrasts with the game’s anime characters.</p>",
